umbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJa5DcsC.jpg&h=aba2347d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aca370Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Faca370Y.jpg&h=1b5dd013&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fQU8zFY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfQU8zFY.jpg&h=c5469ec7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2wsx1kY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2wsx1kY.jpg&h=dcdab03d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ppOtzFY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FppOtzFY.jpg&h=0fa3f5d8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n時間：12:00-18:00<br />\n地區 : 18區<br />\n測試點：<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1IqYnvM0rrG1_lMuLuEZghBqDPBf1WFyw/view?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1IqYnvM0rrG1_lMuLuEZghBqDPBf1WFyw%2Fview%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtN%2FzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=38f56258\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1IqYnvM0rrG1_lMuLuEZghBqDPBf1WFyw/view?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">經濟不景</span></span></strong> <br />\n黃店唔係俾<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">藍店針對就係</span></span></strong><br />\n一間一間捱貴租 <br />\n最後支持唔住<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">一間間咁執</span><br />\n<br />\n如果到最後全香港黃店都企唔住既時候<br />\n你地d醫療物資 防具 食既 全部加價 或者再買唔到既時候<br />\n呢場仗仲點打?<br />\n<br />\n黃店支持我地  <br />\n我地都支持黃店!<br />\n<br />\n10月26  1200全日活動!<br />\n挑戰圍住間黃店座大廈一個圈!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jYZo70W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjYZo70W.jpg&h=6bd6af2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n報料：<br />\n話說而家參加活動都冇人計人數，大家有冇諗過其實可以利用hkmap.live喺全港收集數據？<br />\n<br />\n除咗可以一齊做統計員之外，仲可以趁機練習放哨報哨技術！同埋最最最重要嘅係可以，大家一齊挑戰黃店嘅貨存量！一齊用港幣令黃店提早收檔！<br />\n<br />\n希望手足準時出席6點嘅集會，但如果某d店鋪仲有人龍，都歡迎手足報料。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">數量眾多 食評不盡錄 詳細請睇上面goole文件</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T18:06:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/160852454253838/posts/939311383074604?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F160852454253838%2Fposts%2F939311383074604%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtN%2FzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=e8ca0526\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/160852454253838/posts/939311383074604?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n求加入 朋友舖頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今日探佢話商場成日關 生意真係好差 太古城同將軍澳中心都有舖 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小店來 但本身賣既貨品好有質素 又有咩公平貿易個d 所以租到商場舖<br />\n<br />\n如果絲打買開護膚品化妝品可以網上買又得 去舖頭試又得<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jG8AZQV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjG8AZQV.jpg&h=961f49b9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aGC2EQW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaGC2EQW.png&h=8cadb1b9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RAQ7QXC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRAQ7QXC.jpg&h=6d01702c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ec86802ad6988e7d02047330c5946f9a10b3f4d9","tid":1675154,"uid":15362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T19:19:44.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1b6dcbe996e99e3006ac47fde5d45d2a6133eb6","tid":1675154,"uid":66862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"609a3c5dc2d394c97bf3de6b03289de8c7aea254","tid":1675154,"uid":262489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d71dda710844b9d8703aa18fe8bb9dd7ecaf5e0","tid":1675154,"uid":282534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T16:19:42.000Z","msg":"SUCK 「<strong><span